768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/ewa-manthey/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ewa Manthey</a></em></p> <h2>Aluminium gets a boost from alumina</h2> <p>Aluminium prices have risen lately, driven by record high alumina prices. Alumina prices jumped to a record this year, squeezing profitability for smelters. Prices for the raw material doubled this year, driven by a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180405086/image_180405086.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743776-aluminum-deficit-support-prices-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 11:05:00"}, {"id": "4743772", "title": "VT: Simple Low-Cost Diversification", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2162643372/image_2162643372.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Beautiful planet Earth with night lights of Asian cities views from space. Amazing night planet Earth in view of India, China, Korea and Japan. Development, economics and technology, concept\" data-id=\"2162643372\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2162643372/image_2162643372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2162643372/image_2162643372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2162643372/image_2162643372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2162643372/image_2162643372.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2162643372/image_2162643372.jpg?io=